MTG life & poison counters for Android.

Features:

- life & poison counters
- 1, 2, 3, or 4 players
- history of last changes
- colors to identify players
- low battery consumption
- open source
- free
    - no restrictions
    - no ads (really!)

Please, feel free to send us feedback:

droidmtg@gmail.com

The source code is availabe in GitHub:

https://github.com/mtgdroid/mtg_life
